{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1857917, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 364418, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "用Zhongguo不用China！", "timestamp": 1623752257, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1858219, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 364418, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不如问问为何日本是Japan，不是nihong，riben，iibon", "timestamp": 1623755113, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1858226, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 364418, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "当然有很多历史原因，像是俄语里面的中国接近中文里的“契丹”，你说为什么呢，当然一个国家有权从自己的角度去认识理解并命名另一个国家在本国用语里的名称", "timestamp": 1623755184, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1860858, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 364418, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "匈奴未灭，何以家为", "timestamp": 1623775980, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1864756, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 364418, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "别傻了，还zzxg🙄一个民族的名字有自称和他称之分，而且匈牙利跟匈奴只是恰好音近", "timestamp": 1623837578, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1864802, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 364418, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "公元9世纪，来自7个马扎尔（Magyar）部落和3个卡扎尔（Khazar）部落一同迁徙，合称“十箭”（Onogur），其中On是十，Ogur是箭。大致音变过程：Onogur > Ungarn > Hungary\n再往前推的猜测：马扎尔人原籍乌拉尔或阿尔泰地区，匈奴西迁时一同来到东欧。\n匈牙利语与芬兰语都属于乌拉尔语系。", "timestamp": 1623838033, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 2, "pid": 364418, "reply": 6, "tag": "政治相关", "text": "匈牙利，匈牙利语是Magyarország，按匈牙利语音译应该翻译成马扎尔，为啥要按英语（Hungary）翻译成匈牙利？", "timestamp": 1623752049, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1623838035, "url": "", "vote": {}}}